graph TD
    S([Start]) --> D1{productCount >= maxProducts?}
    D1 -- Yes --> O1[/Display 'Limit Reached'/]
    O1 --> E([Return])
    D1 -- No --> I1[/Input Product Name/]
    I1 --> L1[/Input Price/]
    L1 --> D2{Price < 0?}
    D2 -- Yes --> O2[/Display Invalid/]
    O2 --> L1
    D2 -- No --> L2[/Input Stock/]
    L2 --> D3{Stock < 0?}
    D3 -- Yes --> O3[/Display Invalid/]
    O3 --> L2
    D3 -- No --> P1[Set ID and Active = true]
    P1 --> P2[Store in Array]
    P2 --> C1[[Call saveProductsToFile]]
    C1 --> O4[/Display Success/]
    O4 --> E